Our Voice, Our Rights - MGNREGA Transparency Dashboard

Copyright (c) 2025 Kishore. All rights reserved.

This project is part of the Digital India Initiative, designed to bring 
transparency and accessibility to MGNREGA (Mahatma Gandhi National Rural 
Employment Guarantee Act) performance metrics.

Purpose:
- Track district-wise MGNREGA performance in real-time
- Provide interactive dashboards with trend analysis
- Support low-literacy users with text-to-speech (TTS) functionality
- Enable geolocation-based district selection
- Ensure mobile-first, accessible design

Technology Stack:
- Backend: FastAPI (Python 3.11)
- Frontend: React 18 with Vite 5
- Database: PostgreSQL 15
- Cache: Redis 7
- Containerization: Docker & Docker Compose

Data Source: data.gov.in (MGNREGA API)

For questions or contributions, please contact:
